TASK_ID=32
TASK_TITLE=Redesign Quick Actions cards with elegant Charmbracelet styling
TASK_STATUS=done
TASK_CREATED=1743292800
TASK_TYPE=feature
TASK_DESCRIPTION=The Quick Actions section in the TUI needs a visual overhaul. Current cards lack elegance. Requirements: (1) Follow all Charmbracelet/Lip Gloss best practices for card components — proper padding, borders, subtle colors, consistent spacing. (2) Each card must have both a TITLE and a DESCRIPTION line. (3) Replace current icons with elegant, tasteful Unicode icons appropriate for each action. (4) Cards should feel premium — think clean whitespace, soft borders, good typography hierarchy between title and description. Look at how Charm's official apps (e.g. Glow, Soft Serve) style their list items and cards for inspiration. The Quick Actions cards were recently redesigned in task-31 as vertical card buttons — this is a refinement pass on that work.
TASK_TAGS=tui,dashboard
